@dsyme does this happen with both SkiaSharp.Svg 1.60.0 and 1.59.1?

I don't think there will be any fixes merged for SkiaSharp.Svg.

This library may be the way to go: https://github.com/wieslawsoltes/Svg.Skia . The overall project is to convert https://github.com/vvvv/SVG to netstandard (https://github.com/vvvv/SVG/issues/590) and then give it more renderers, of which https://github.com/wieslawsoltes/Svg.Skia is one.
